     :Y-OR-N
          A yes or no question returning T or NIL.
     :VARIABLE
          A lisp variable
     :FUNCTION
          A lisp function
     :COMMAND
          A stumpwm command as a string.
     :KEY-SEQ
          A key sequence starting from *TOP-MAP*
     :WINDOW-NUMBER
          An existing window number
     :NUMBER
          An integer number
     :STRING
          A string
     :KEY
          A single key chord
     :WINDOW-NAME
          An existing window’s name
     :DIRECTION
